description:
Back by popular demand, Allison Janney (Mom, The West Wing...and basically Queen of the Damn World, ugh) returns to Unqualified!  Allison talks about getting her star on the Hollywood walk of fame and preparing for her Broadway debut. She also meets Karen Sarducci and auditions for a new (and bizarre) HBO show. Then Sim and Allison fight it out in a new game called Who Knows Anna Best? Come back tomorrow for Part 2 when the gang hits the phones for some listener calls!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
